Alright, monkeyed with the picture and the full size can be seen by right-clicking and Viewing Image

Also to clarify ahead of time, I added the tag "sympathetic" not because the plants were nice and sweet but because the core behavior of this SCP is that it affected the world around it and the plants within it in a sympathetic manner. When things were good in the greenhouse, things were good in the whole neighborhood. Likewise the plants were just as nurturing and kind as their gardeners — which unfortunately meant they weren't above pruning the research staff when they felt like it.







